NEWS

Demon Slayer

Demon Slayer follows the story of Tanjiro, a young boy whose family is tragically killed by demons, and his younger sister, Nezuko, who becomes a demon herself. Determined to avenge his family and find a cure for Nezuko, Tanjiro joins the Demon Slayer Corps and the latest episode is all set to be released on Sunday. For those who are not a fan of subtitles, the wait is over. The English dub of Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Sword-smith Village Arc (also known as season 3) has been confirmed and a release date has been announced.
